# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TalentScout Hiring Assistant — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# 1. Copy this file:  cp .env.example .env
# 2. Fill in whichever API keys you have (at least ONE required)
# 3. NEVER commit the .env file to version control
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Option A: Anthropic Claude ────────────────────────────────
# Get key from: https://console.anthropic.com
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-your-key-here

# ── Option B: Google Gemini 2.5 Flash ────────────────────────
# Get key from: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=AIza-your-key-here

# ── Option C: Groq (Llama-3.3-70b) ───────────────────────────
# Get key from: https://console.groq.com  (free tier available!)
GROQ_API_KEY=gsk_your-key-here
